## Enrollment Status

Students are required to be registered for 12 or more units to be considered enrolled *full-time *in the Fall, Spring, or Summer semesters. For the purposes of Financial Aid (including loan deferments) and enrollment reporting, Make School defines enrollment status as:

Full Time:	12 or more units

Three-Quarter Time:	9 - 11.9 units

Half Time:	6 - 8.9 units

Less than Half Time:	0 - 5.9 units

For further information regarding how enrollment status affects you, or to get help regarding submitting a deferment request, contact the [Office of the Registrar](mailto:registrar@makeschool.com).
